item.title: Contact Info
item.description: If there’s stuff that doesn’t quite make sense or seems wrong, feel free to send me a message! While I’ll try to respond as soon as I can, do note that there are a lot of resources online that can help as well. Here are a few ways to contact me: Find me on the EV Slack! Send a DM, or to the channel #wmc-questions or #omc-questions. Email: jyim1120@gmail.
